<view class="network-config-page data-v-43f32807"><view class="notice-box data-v-43f32807"><text class="notice-text data-v-43f32807">*注：手机需开启WiFi功能，Android手机还需开启 定位 功能。</text><text class="notice-text data-v-43f32807">*注：仅支持连接2.4GHz频段的WiFi 。</text></view><view class="form-item data-v-43f32807"><view class="label-row data-v-43f32807"><text class="label-required data-v-43f32807">*</text><text class="label-text data-v-43f32807">WiFi名称：</text></view><view class="input-row data-v-43f32807"><input class="wifi-input data-v-43f32807" placeholder="请输入WiFi名称" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','wifiName','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{wifiName}}" bindinput="__e"/><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['getCurrentWifi',['$event']]]]]}}" class="get-wifi-btn data-v-43f32807" bindtap="__e">获取当前WiFi</button></view></view><view class="form-item data-v-43f32807"><view class="label-row data-v-43f32807"><text class="label-text data-v-43f32807">WiFi密码：</text></view><view class="password-wrapper data-v-43f32807"><input class="wifi-input password-input data-v-43f32807" password="{{!showPassword}}" placeholder="请输入密码" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','wifiPassword','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{wifiPassword}}" bindinput="__e"/><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['togglePassword',['$event']]]]]}}" class="eye-icon data-v-43f32807" bindtap="__e"><uni-icons vue-id="3a7259df-1" type="{{showPassword?'eye-filled':'eye-slash-filled'}}" size="24" color="#666" class="data-v-43f32807" bind:__l="__l"></uni-icons></view></view></view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['useLastConfig',['$event']]]]]}}" class="last-config-btn data-v-43f32807" bindtap="__e"><text class="last-config-text data-v-43f32807">使用上次配置的WiFi名称和密码</text></view><view class="action-buttons data-v-43f32807"><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['resetNetwork',['$event']]]]]}}" class="reset-btn data-v-43f32807" bindtap="__e">重置设备网络</button